title: The Children's Book
description:
Housecat - The Children’s Book
AUG 01 2021 - All streaming platforms

The Children’s Book is a concept album created by Housecat. The album focuses on topics such as growing up, personal development, individuation and the spirit of childhood. With an overarching spiritual quality, the album is made for having fun and laughing. “I want to make an album where someone can hit play and get taken into this joyous and surreal dream-like world in which everyone gets to be a kid again.”
